    • RGB and CW Parameter:14W(1200LM). PETEME WiFi recessed lighting supports cool white & warm white from 2700K to 6500K, providing 16 million colors. You can use the APP to adjust different colors to match your different demands.
    • Voice Control:The smart led recessed lighting 6 inch is compatible with Alexa and Google Assistant. Use simple dialogue to control the ceiling light fixture and release your hands. You can control them by sound in a moment.
    • Sync with Music:PETEME color changing lights can synchronize with music to make wonderful atmosphere. After connecting to the Smart Life App, you can set the home management to control the led recessed lighting in the whole house with your families.
    • APP Intelligent Control:1.Download Smart Life APP. 2.Select automatic search, connect to the hub 3.The hub will automatically search for downlights and then select the connection. The led lights can work with Alexa and be controlled remotely. 4.Only Support 2.4 GHz WiFi frequency band signal.
    • IC Rated & Easy Install:The Canless LED recessed light is IC rated,allowing contact with the insulation layer in the ceiling, which means that the junction box is thermally protected.This Recessed lighting has ETL certification, energy star certification, FCC certification and other relevant safety certification.

    • Austin
      5.0 out of 5 starsVerified Purchase
      Great lights but not the most user friendly app
      Reviewed in the United States on June 10, 2024
      Color: 6 InchSize: 6 Count (Pack of 1)
      0:05
      I ordered these Smart LED recessed lights to replace the generic ones in the front of my house. They were reasonably priced with the coupon available at the time I purchased them and once I got them installed, they were just what I was looking for. They are very bright but... See more
      I ordered these Smart LED recessed lights to replace the generic ones in the front of my house. They were reasonably priced with the coupon available at the time I purchased them and once I got them installed, they were just what I was looking for. They are very bright but can be dimmed to a level that youre comfortable with and youre able to change them to any color you want.

      I will say the app these lights use (Smart Life) is not very intuitive in my opinion. Although grouping multiple lights together so they can be controlled all at once is possible, I found it very difficult to figure out how to do that. Theres a video on the product listing that helps but it just seems kind of backwards on how this functionality is setup.

      These lights do use a mesh gateway to control them so just know that small piece of equipment needs to be remained plugged in somewhere fairly close to the lights while still close to a wifi signal.

      I like how low profile they are and snug up tightly to the ceiling. They didnt have a foam ring included to serve as a barrier for bugs to get in while installed outside on the soffit. I found a caulk cord weather seal to help with this.

      One problem I ran into was installing one of the lights close to the rafter. It was difficult to fit back into the precut hole because the LED box on the back of the light was slightly deeper than the non-smart one originally installed.

      Overall Im happy with these lights and how theyve enhanced our curb appeal. The price, ease of install, and quality have made it a great purchase.
      7 people found this helpful
